RecordMismatch is a Form
    is primary
    restrict action OpenRecord
    Layout
        paragraph
            ReplicationSet
            RepSetBC
            RepSetBC.BusinessClass
                no label
                align as label
                display as text
        paragraph
            RepSetBCValidationResult
            RepSetBCValidationResult.ValidationEndTime
            RepSetBCValidationResult.LastRefreshStamp
            RepSetBCVRRecordMismatch
                label is "ID"
        paragraph
            visible when (RecordUniqueID entered)
                RecordUniqueID
            Keys
                show up to 100 characters
            visible when (OpenRecordValid)
                button of "OpenRecord"
                    action is OpenRecord
            visible when (RecordTouchValid)
                visible when (RepSetBC.BusinessClass.HasUpdateStamp)
                    CurrentTimeStamp
                WillReplicateNextRun
                button of "IncludeInNextReplication"
                    action is TouchRecord
            MismatchType
        paragraph
            Notes
                use text area of 5 lines
        text of "CheckSumResults"
            bold
        CheckSumResults
